---
title: Sweet Potato and Quinoa Bowl with Avocado and Orange-Balsamic Dressing
description: Dinner tonight is full of amazing veggies! Roasted sweet potatoes, creamy avocado and tangy arugula are drizzled with a citrusy orange-balsamic dressing. Perfect cooked quinoa is the perfect final touch to this colourful bowl!
